<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Loose Women star Nadia Sawalha played Kim Kardashian for laughs once again on Wednesday after stripping down to her underwear in a body positive video. </p>

<p>The TV panelist, 55, mimicked a voice-over of American entrepreneur Kim discussing her hugely popular range of SKIMS undergarments while posing in a mismatched bra and knickers. </p>

<p>With Kim's disembodied voice heard talking about the benefits of body contouring shape-wear, Nadia mimed along in a video parody shared with her 312,000 Instagram followers. </p>

<p>Here we go: Loose Women star Nadia Sawalha played Kim Kardashian for laughs on Wednesday after stripping down to her underwear in a body positive video</p>

<p>It is the second time Nadia has mimicked Kim after previously miming to one of her underwear commercials in August.  </p>

